Former DA leader Helen Zille has come to the rescue of a domestic violence victim in Mthatha struggling to receive proper healthcare. Wendy Mjijima, 25, was assaulted allegedly by her boyfriend, an attack which left her with a broken jaw.Speaking to the Daily Dispatch, Mjijima said the incident happened on Saturday evening, after which she was rushed to a nearby clinic in Ngqeleni.For the full story get a copy of the Dispatch or subscribe to our e-Edition for the complete newspaper with jobs, classifieds, crosswords, TV schedules and back editions&nbsp;